**At the end:** Overall hire recommendation (Yes/Maybe/No), Perceived level (Medior/Senior/Staff), Critical fixes before sending to recruiters, One uncomfortable truth.

**Tone:** Direct, professional, honest. No generic praise. No design trend commentary.
